content: My 24th Anniversary at Fox 5 News! It's hard to believe it's been 24 years!! I've worked with some Great people Like camerawoman Brenda Rivera ( seen in picture) covering majors news events across the country and the world.   I've been Blessed to travel to Israel, Guatemala, Costa Rica and England... interviewing Leaders like Israeli Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu.   I even got to ring the opening bell at the New York Stock Exchange & Nasdaq.  And THANK YOU Fox 5 viewers for watching us and saying so many kind things when I see you on the streets!! You are the BEST!! ( and what about All those hair styles! What was I thinking üòÄ)
